         <div xml:lang="en" type="translation">
            <ab>Year 1. [- - -], son(?) of Sambas, has paid to Hermes, son of Aphrodisios, who has in charge the monodesmia of hay on sheep [of the village of Karanis(?)] for the first year the [- - -] on sheep and other animals: [in Pharmouthi(?)] sixteen drachmai, equal 16 drachmai; in Pachon [further] sixteen drachmai, equal 16 drachmai; in Pauni further sixteen [drachmai], equal 16 drachmai</ab>
         </div>
